Components: core-libs
Sub-Component: java.sql
Synopsis:JDBC 4.2 introducing the following features

Adition of REF_CURSOR support

Addition of the java.sql.DriverAction Interface
Addition of the security check on deregisterDriver Method in DriverManager Class
Addition of the java.sql.SQLType Interface
Addition of the javva.sql.JDBCType Enum
